@startuml
title Session State Machine

[*] --> Idle
Idle --> Pairing: pair-setup
Pairing --> Verified: pair-verify ok
Pairing --> Error: auth failed
Verified --> Configured: SETUP ok
Configured --> Streaming: RECORD or play
Streaming --> Flushing: FLUSH
Flushing --> Streaming: flush complete
Streaming --> TearingDown: TEARDOWN
Configured --> TearingDown: TEARDOWN
TearingDown --> Closed
Error --> Closed
Closed --> [*]

@enduml
